Developer Terms of Use
des:
Our team at West Loop Strategy loves the Chicago Bulls and since we can't hop on the court for more than one reason we created Last Dance - Unofficial to re-live the glory days. Test your knowledge of the 90s Chicago Bulls Players and have fun reliving facts about the Bulls.

To start, just say "Alexa, play last dance" or "Alexa, open last dance", or "Alexa start a quiz with last dance"

At anytime, you can stop the game by saying "Alexa, stop"
